<A>__{the room bursts out with an accumulated fury at the young oswald a tremendous release of tension. on the tv we see the excitement in the newsmen's eyes; they all sense that this is the break they're looking for in the case. garrison and ivon watch the tv, and then garrison stands and pays the bill.}
